               <p>LYON LEVY. I live at <placeName id="t18100718-69-crimeloc415">16, York-street, Covent-garden</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18100718-69-crimeloc415" type="placeName" value="16, York-street, Covent-garden"></interp>
