                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18100718-69-off413 t18100718-69-crimeloc415"></join>. On the 29th of June, I lost the coat from the inside of the shop; it was one of my wearing coats, I heard a cry of stop thief; I saw a man running, the coat was picked up by a strange man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18100718-69-person705">
                  HENRY 
                  HOWARD
